properties.headline: Tornado Watch issued January 11 at 6:33PM EST until January 11 at 9:00PM EST by NWS Tallahassee FL
properties.description:

INCLUDE THE FOLLOWING AREAS UNTIL 9 PM EST THIS EVENING

IN FLORIDA THIS WATCH INCLUDES 3 COUNTIES

IN THE BIG BEND OF FLORIDA

FRANKLIN              GADSDEN               LIBERTY

IN GEORGIA THIS WATCH INCLUDES 4 COUNTIES

IN SOUTH CENTRAL GEORGIA

WORTH

IN SOUTHWEST GEORGIA

DECATUR               GRADY                 MITCHELL

BAINBRIDGE, BAY CITY, BEACHTON, BEVERLY, BRANCHVILLE,

MITCHELL CO A/P, MONCRIEF, PELHAM, PINE PARK, QUINCY,
